ets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n「男人唔俾入女廁，男人點樣界定？？？」 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n班liberals又會出黎話<br />\n&quot;我地需要輸入呢D人因為低技術工種無本地人肯做&quot;<br />\n我又想問，既然係咁點解唔要求公司加人工加福利去吸引本地人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<del>中產家庭出世大學讀gender studies/social science成世都未返過工中學時期被人排斥無朋友所以大學要扮英雄去拯救自己腦中低賤人種</del>既liberals唔係最鐘意出黎爭取福利爭取加人工架咩?</blockquote><br />\n輸入外地人去被資本家剝削，然後本地人繼續失業，大家都無好結果。見到班退步左派真係笑撚咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b4ce17053fa223c118264a3dc54cf2f82bd0928","tid":358783,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T04:20:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲未有左膠可以解釋點解無啦啦要拆左Robert Lee個雕像引發今次示威</blockquote><br />\n唔方便嘅事實，班新共產主義者點會題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45e37016e6d5f47dd03923248c96780c4872d33e","tid":358783,"uid":86841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T04:22:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1d61864bd3004b9cc351fdae991931122225b395","tid":358783,"uid":59518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T04:22:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你叫班自命神聖係低賤人種拯救者既白畜liberals情何以堪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n全世界嘅左翼，由共產到大愛，都係智障架喇<br />\n<br />\n佢哋咪又係繼續話你哋咩咩歧視呀，咩咩民族主義分離主義呀，咩咩大家都係一家人呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n班右翼無人性，就係到批評左翼大愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />