ir &ldquo;heritage,&rdquo; and outright white nationalists.<br />\n<br />\nIn Charlottesville, advocates targeted a statue of Robert E. Lee in a park called Lee Square &mdash; <strong>City Council members pointed out that Lee had no connection to Charlottesville, implying that commemorating him was just an indirect way to celebrate the Confederacy</strong>, while a high-school student collected 600 signatures on a <a href=\"http://Change.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FChange.org&d=IQQLIalogHytNZHrV13Rnp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=68d70e84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Change.org</a> petition to rename the statue. (A counter-petition collected 2,000 signatures.)<br />\n<br />\nIn February, the city council voted to sell the statue and rename the park Emancipation Park. (The statue is still in place.)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.vox.com/2017/8/12/16138246/charlottesville-nazi-rally-right-uva\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vox.com%2F2017%2F8%2F12%2F16138246%2Fcharlottesville-nazi-rally-right-uva&d=IQQLIalogHytNZHrV13Rnp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=405959d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.vox.com/2017/8/12/16138246/charlottesville-nazi-rally-right-uva</a>"},{"pid":"7dc7b3bed5ce1f5c345d97b7e3f3f32656e940ea","tid":358783,"uid":131691,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T04:55:02.000Z","msg":"個左膠啞咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07178ae42272b2431dc1e540ef9c6f5e3fcad7a7","tid":358783,"uid":86841,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T04:56:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7bc3ff18dc5342a0b8463688e6d9b3f9822ba13c","tid":358783,"uid":131691,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T05:17:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>個左膠啞咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又一件冇人性on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"h